thread.title: BRIEF-NP3 Fastigheter Q4 Profit From Property Management Up At SEK 78‍​ Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-NP3 Fastigheter Q4 Profit From Property Management Up At SEK 78‍​ Mln
text:
Feb 23 (Reuters) - Np3 Fastigheter Ab:
* Q4 RENTAL INCOME SEK ‍​ 180 MILLION VERSUS SEK 154 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q4 PROFIT FROM PROPERTY MANAGEMENT SEK 78‍​ MILLION VERSUS SEK 75 MILLION YEAR AGO
* BOARD PROPOSES A DIVIDEND FOR 2017 OF SEK 2.70 / ORDINARY SHARE‍​
* BOARD PROPOSES FY DIVIDEND OF SEK 2.00 / PREFERENCE SHARE WITH QUARTERLY PAYMENT OF SEK 0.50 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
